title: News about Cyberpunk 2077 romance options
body:
That’s a response from Lead Quest Designer for CP2077 Paweł Sasko. So we can expect entire quest/plot lines for romances, there’s multiple genders/orientations to go from like they said previously, and more importantly those romances matter to the story over all. 

My only question: can we romance the Animal leader Sasquatch?

question: 🍓 Gimme that Kasumi content!
answer:
ask and ye shall receive!

Kasumi is very childlike in nature. She’s immature, and some would even describe her as a little troll. She does not take anything seriously. You can most often find her in the dungeon that she calls home, either scouring the web for information to sell or playing in online competitive matches in various PVP matches. Socially inept and zany, only a few people can deal with her eccentric nature.

(imagine this but darker lmao ^)

Currently, her hermit like tendencies have amplified as she copes with her recent divorce from Nyx ( @cyberneticfallout​‘s OC - THAT’S YOU BB ) and the reemergence of a individual from her past (oc i’m currently working on ^^’).
